deps.context: find_package(qt 6.2 names qt6 components core required)
find_package(qt 5.12 names qt5 components core required)

find_package(qt${qt_version_major}
  components
    concurrent
    core
    gui
    network
    opengl
    printsupport
    qml
    quickwidgets
    sql
    svg
    test
    widgets
    xml
    ${qt6_new_components}
  required
)
find_package(ffmpeg components libavcodec libavformat libavutil libswresample)

libs.content:
find_library(mp3lame_library
  names mp3lame mp3lame-static
  doc "lame library"
)

find_library(fftw_library
  names fftw fftw3 fftw-3.3
  doc "fftw library"
)

find_library(portmidi_library
  names portmidi portmidi_s
  doc "portmidi library"
)

find_program(llvmar_executable
  names llvm-ar
  doc "the llvm-ar executable"
  )

find_program(llvmnm_executable
  names llvm-nm
  doc "the llvm-nm executable"
  )

find_program(llvmranlib_executable
  names llvm-ranlib
  doc "the llvm-ranlib executable"
  )
